 {"id":"asupersync-1qfd0.303","title":"Batch 301: 6 io/ext + copy + lines files audited — all SOUND, zero bugs. Files: src/io/ext/mod.rs (29L), src/io/ext/seek_ext.rs (203L), src/io/ext/read_ext.rs (~36KB), src/io/ext/write_ext.rs (~25KB), src/io/copy.rs (~44KB), src/io/lines.rs (219L). Key patterns: completed flags on all futures, cooperative yield counters (>32), fail-closed repoll guards, incremental UTF-8 validation in ReadToString, CopyBuf un-marks completed if final flush pending.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-13T01:44:47.270144992Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-13T01:44:47.270144992Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"asupersync-1qfd0.303","depends_on_id":"asupersync-1qfd0","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-13T01:44:47.270144992Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
 {"id":"asupersync-1qfd0.304","title":"Batch 302: 7 io files audited — all SOUND, zero bugs. Files: src/io/cap.rs (2826L), src/io/read.rs (410L), src/io/read_buf.rs (91L), src/io/seek.rs (53L), src/io/split.rs (344L), src/io/write.rs (408L), src/io/mod.rs (105L). Key patterns: capability-based default-deny authority system with 6 IoCap sub-traits, builder dedup guards, Chain reads avoid false EOF on full buffer, Take limit uses saturating_sub, RefCell-based read/write split.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-13T01:46:06.590577574Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-13T01:46:06.590577574Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"asupersync-1qfd0.304","depends_on_id":"asupersync-1qfd0","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-13T01:46:06.590577574Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
 {"id":"asupersync-1qfd0.305","title":"Batch 303: 6 io files audited — all SOUND, zero bugs. Files: read_line.rs (598L), stream_adapters.rs (378L), write_permit.rs (247L), buf_reader.rs (462L), buf_writer.rs (525L), record/mod.rs (33L). ReadLine split-UTF8+CRLF normalization+cooperative yield. StreamReader defers errors. WritePermit two-phase commit. BufWriter tracks partial flush via written field.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-13T01:46:41.621983518Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-13T01:46:41.621983518Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"asupersync-1qfd0.305","depends_on_id":"asupersync-1qfd0","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-13T01:46:41.621983518Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
